sources.title: Menace from Outer Space (1954) ROCKY JONES, SPACE RANGER
sources.description:
Stars: Richard Crane, Robert Lyden, Sally Mansfield
Director: Hollingsworth Morse

You've heard of The Lone Ranger, now meet The Space Ranger!

Follow the adventures of Rocky Jones and crew as they cruise the galaxy in their Orbit Jet X-V2 and defend Earth against space-bound evil doers!

sources.title: Rocky Jones, Space Ranger - Menace from Outer Space
sources.description: Cruising the galaxy in his space ship "The Orbit Jet" Space Ranger, Rocky Jones (Richard Crane), Vena Ray (Sally Mansfield), and 10 year-old Bobby (Robert Lyden) defend the Earth and themselves against space-bound evil doers. A couple of missiles strike earth and Rocky and the gang go to find out where they are coming from. They end up on a moon of Jupiter which is perfect for their survival. They are lucky to land because they have run out of gas. At least their gas gauge says so.
